Feature: Product Search

  Scenario: Search for existing product
    Given I am on the home page
    When I search for "MacBook"
    Then I should see products related to "MacBook"

  Scenario: Search for non-existing product
    Given I am on the home page
    When I search for "XYZ123"
    Then I should see "No products found"

    Feature: Product Filters

      Scenario: Filter products by category
        Given I am on the product catalog page
        When I filter by "Laptops"
        Then I should see only products in "Laptops"